== Other versions of the legendarium ==
In [[The Quenta]], '''Haleth the Hunter''' was the son of [[Hador]] who first appears as one of the Fathers of Men.<ref>{{SM|Q9}}, p. 104.</ref> Later, he appeared as the leader of one of the Three Houses of Men,<ref>See e.g. {{GA|122}} (born in Eriador in F.A. 388); {{GA|129}} (comes into Beleriand with his people); {{GA|126}} (his son Hundor born in F.A. 413).</ref> until his character was reworked into Lady Haleth.<ref>{{WJ|14}}, p. 227-228.</ref>

